abstract: >-
  A forensic framework for treating AI system prompts as governance artifacts.
  This project provides a methodology to normalize, analyze, and compare
  system prompts across major AI assistants, decomposing them into modular
  Prompt Governance Primitives (PGPs) to surface architectural trade-offs
  and control mechanisms.
